HEADWORD: Copernican
<hw>Co*per"ni*can</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to
Copernicus, a Prussian by birth (<it>b.</it> 1473, <it>d.</it> 1543),
who taught the world the solar system now received, called the
<xex>Copernican</xex> system.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

